WEBVTT

00:06.363 --> 00:06.915
Hello?

00:07.479 --> 00:08.962
Hi, is this Danny McGrath?

00:09.355 --> 00:09.612
Yeah.

00:10.859 --> 00:14.153
The Danny McGrath who graduated from Knibb High School in 1984?

00:15.060 --> 00:16.747
Uh, yeah. Who's this?

00:17.629 --> 00:19.141
Um, this is Billy Madison.

00:19.513 --> 00:22.407
You probably don't remember me, but I went to high school with you.

00:23.633 --> 00:26.462
I kinda gave you a hard time back then,...

00:26.557 --> 00:30.169
...and then I did some things that I thought were funny at the time,...

00:30.365 --> 00:33.704
...but now I realize they were just mean and stupid,...

00:33.823 --> 00:37.488
...and I just wanted to apologize, and I hope you forgive me.

00:38.076 --> 00:39.382
Yeah, sure. Don't worry about it.

00:39.479 --> 00:39.995
It's no problem.

00:40.901 --> 00:42.160
Wow! That's great!

00:43.694 --> 00:48.901
Well, I am sorry, and maybe we can get together sometime and have some coffee or something.

00:49.617 --> 00:50.512
Sure, I'd like that.

00:50.957 --> 00:52.713
OK. Well, I'll see you around.

00:53.023 --> 00:54.537
OK. Bye.

